 88→ *
 89→ * Validates file client-side, uploads CSV to backend for parsing and import.
 90→ * Supports comma, semicolon, tab delimiters; case-insensitive headers;
 91→ * scientific notation account IDs; and partial success (skips invalid rows).
 92→ *
 93→ * @param file CSV file with user mappings
 94→ * @returns ImportResult with counts and error details
 95→ * @throws Error if upload fails or validation errors occur
